# websockets is a transitive of google-genai (which declares <17,>=13). It is NOT used
# in prod (we call only generate_content/list/embed, never the Live API). Cap at <16 so
# the prod pin matches the dev RAGAS tree (langgraph-sdk requires websockets<16) and the
# shared-dep gate (ci_check.check_requirements) passes without bumping the prod tree for
# a dev-only eval. See #347.
websockets<16
